    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. Mechanically, it is sound with a smooth engine and responsive transmission. The interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only light wear consistent with regular use. On the exterior, the paint still shines, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and one small scratch on the rear passenger door. All electronics and features are fully functional. It is a reliable, solid car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
