      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle in good overall condition. The exterior paint still shines beautifully, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with regular use. Inside, the leather seats are in great shape with no rips or tears, and all electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has a complete service history, and the tires have plenty of tread left. It drives smoothly, shifts gears without hesitation, and has been recently inspected to ensure reliability. This is a solid, honest car that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
