    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that\u2019s full of character! This car has been a faithful companion and is in honest, fair condition. While it shows some well-earned signs of use both inside and out, it still delivers a solid driving experience and is eager for its next adventure. If you're looking for a practical, budget-friendly vehicle that gets the job done with a smile, this is the one for you!",
