    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard and presented in showroom condition. Every detail of this automobile, from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments, reflects a level of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. This unit represents a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast seeking a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery state. Meticulously inspected and certified, it stands as a testament to automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
