    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely zero swirls, stone chips, or imperfections, complemented by perfectly preserved alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from the day it left the dealership; the premium leather is supple and free of creases, while the dashboard and trim pieces show no signs of UV exposure or wear. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history and a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and even smells brand new. No detail has been overlooked in its care, making it one of the finest examples currently available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
